name: "mistake"
description: It was an accident ! I didn’t want to kill him . I was sick and tired of my dad , All he did was drink and swear, he would beat my mother every day , I was tired of him, but I didn’t want to be a murderer , I was just punching him and I could feel my fists smashing his face , my brain didn’t approve of it , but my fists didn't care.
